# Virtualenvs / build artifacts — nested (bare patterns above match root only)
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.egg-info/

# Not needed at runtime — these dirs are COPY'd wholesale into the image via the
# editable source packages, so excluding them shrinks both context and image.
# (READMEs are kept: pyproject `readme = "README.md"` is read at build time.)
**/tests/
**/docs/
inference_models/examples/
**/dockerfiles/
inference_models/development/
mkdocs.yml
**/pytest.ini
